  "description": "A cosy south-west facing, 2-bed apartment in the ideal location, perfect for a family looking for a relaxing and fun holiday in the heart of Marbella.\n\nUpon entering (up a flight of stairs), you have the open plan kitchen/dining/living area with a fully equipped kitchen with a breakfast bar, a dining area for 4, and a lounge area with a smart TV. This leads to the terrace with an outdoor dining table and views over the gardens, onto the mountains.\n\nThere is a Master Bedroom with a double bed and ensuite bathroom with shower. Bedroom 2 is a twin room. There is a further bathroom with a shower.\n\nThe apartment offers individual aircon units in each room, wifi throughout, and a secure parking space outside the apartment.\n\nSet in generous community gardens with a large pool, a separate pool for children, a tennis court and 24-hour security, Andalucia Garden Club Apartment is a great choice for your holidays in Marbella.\n\nAndalucia Garden Club is extremely well located. Only 5 minutes walk to Puerto Banús and the beaches, it is also only 200 metres away from the popular Centro Plaza shopping centre, home to the Saturday market.\n\nIt is a great option for families looking for a comfortable and convenient base within walking distance to amenities.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you.",
